cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.SI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language modeling and speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a probabilistic parameterization and an expectation-maximization algorithm for training the model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper presents an original approach to language modeling. 
- cs.SD (Sound) and cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper deals with speech recognition and word lattice rescoring.
